data.description: Must See Property situated in a Gorgeous Private Gated Community in the Highland Estates. This beautiful home a Two Story property with Double Door Entry with Grand Dual Stairway Casing. Subject has Open Designed Kitchen that features center island and holds stainless steel appliances, built-in microwave, stainless steel dual wall double oven, tile flooring, with walk-in pantry. This home has 4 bedrooms with 4 full bathrooms and all rooms also have walk-in closets. Plantation Shutters throughout entire home, with porcelain tile flooring, ceiling fans throughout home.  Master bedroom with Retreat that also entertains vault ceiling. Must not forget Private Home Office !   The backyard contains a cozy well landscaped scenery, Mantled Fireplace, Outdoor Stoned Kitchen for entertainment.  Newly Purchased Solar Systems / with Tesla Battery Charger and  also New A/C Unit recently installed Garage.  Tandem garage entertain as Private Gym  at your pleasure.  This amazing home want last long !!!!!
